articles.author: James Farrell
articles.title: Eurovision Song Contest: Israel Makes Finals As Protests Continue - Forbes
articles.description: Israeli singer Eden Golan has become the center of controversy as protests against the Israel-Hamas war continue on.
articles.content: Israeli singer Eden Golan advanced to the final round of the Eurovision song competition and will sing later Saturday, as thousands of pro-Palestinian demonstrators continue to protest in the events … [+4261 chars]
